/* Notepad++ HexEditor — French (fr)
 *
 * Full translation. Keys mirror Localizable.en.strings; comments stay in
 * English so future translators can diff against the canonical source.
 *
 * Format specifiers (%@, %d, %zu, %lu, %1$d, %1$@, etc.) are preserved
 * verbatim — re-ordering positional args is the translator's job. The
 * "N⁠o⁠t⁠e⁠p⁠a⁠d⁠+⁠+" form embeds U+2060 Word Joiners and must be copied
 * byte-for-byte from the English source (see about.body).
 *
 * GitHub URLs are hard-coded — never localize the URL itself, only the
 * surrounding label text.
 */

